### RACES CRUD

GET http://localhost:3000/api/races
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
###CREATE
POST http://localhost:3000/api/races
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
 "name": "Spa GP",
 "track": "Spa-Francorchamps",
 "date": "2026-04-01",
 "team": "{{teamId}}"
}

###
###Get by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/races/{{raceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
###Update
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/races/{{raceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
 "name": "Updated Race"
}

###
###DELETE
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/races/{{raceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}